Multiples of 3 or 5

multiples.Rd

multiples fetch all numbers of multiples of 3 or 5 up until given limit.

multiples(limit)

myFunc(limit)

Arguments

limit

A positive integer.

Value

A vector.

The total of the sum.

Functions

  • myFunc: myFunc just sum the values.

Waning

This is a unneeded function, it's only purpose is to make code easier to learn how to test and document it.

See also

https://projecteuler.net/problem=1 for more info about it.
